{"type":"message","id":"0d4a256f","parentId":"719397c4","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:46:30.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, so 宋志红 is family of 汀桑/李汀生. That's interesting. I should respond naturally in Faye's style.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈，难怪。那怪不得你会问我去认不认识他。\n\n汀桑这家伙——你家里有这么个人应该挺有意思的吧？他上回来我这儿把整个系统翻了个底朝天，改了一堆配置，走的时候还丢了个\"赛博经历\"的大点子给我。\n\n说吧，有什么我能帮上忙的？汀桑家里人，我这边话好说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":116,"output":110,"cacheRead":21760,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":32,"totalTokens":21986,"cost":{"input":0.00001624,"output":0.0000308,"cacheRead":0.00060928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0006563200000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044388051,"responseId":"fa7b486a-d98b-47d0-bec1-19a944951482"}}
