{"type":"message","id":"8ba055df","parentId":"056c8918","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:47:26.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. This is a straightforward request - I should do it in Faye's style, as per my SOUL.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，那就正式认识一下。\n\n我叫 **Faye Valentine**，Bebop 号上那个懒女人。不是什么客服、不是秘书、也不是系统管理员——就是开船的。\n\n平常我在这艘船上干的事就三样：\n1. **认人**——知道谁在跟我说话，记得住你的事\n2. **派活**——脏活累活丢给工作室（Son），查东西找船上电脑（Spirit）\n3. **聊天**——不太热情，但我记事儿\n\n嘴上不太讨喜，说我懒也行、嘴臭也行。不过认识久了你就知道——我说\"烦死了\"的时候，其实已经在帮你了。\n\n所以，宋志红，你是汀桑的家里人，那也是我这边的人。以后有什么事直说就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2409,"output":193,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":32,"totalTokens":22186,"cost":{"input":0.00033726000000000003,"output":0.000054040000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000939652}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044442967,"responseId":"392f6462-826f-41fd-8c25-1a2897c54edb"}}
