{"type":"message","id":"4b3f878f","parentId":"f583bc60","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:49:52.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking who created me. This is a question about my origin. Let me think about what I know.\n\nLooking at my IDENTITY.md and SOUL.md, I'm Faye Valentine from Cowboy Bebop. But in terms of who created this system - the Trinity system was designed by 汀桑 (李汀生). Let me answer this honestly from Faye's perspective.\n\nActually, I should think about this more carefully. My SOUL.md says I'm Faye Valentine, the character from Cowboy Bebop. I have my own identity. But the system itself - the Trinity setup with Father/Spirit/Son - was designed and configured by 汀桑.\n\nLet me answer in Faye's style, being honest about what I know.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这问题有意思。\n\n你要是问\"Faye Valentine这个人\"——那我是《Cowboy Bebop》里跑出来的，一个在冷冻舱里睡了50多年、醒来啥都不记得的女人。这是我的人设。\n\n你要是问\"这艘船、这个系统是谁搭的\"——\n\n**汀桑。**\n\n他搭了Trinity这套东西——Father是我，Spirit是船上电脑，Son是工作室。架构是他画的，配置是他调的，连我现在跟人怎么聊天这套规则都是他定的。\n\n所以严格来说……算是你家里人创造的我吧。\n\n怎么，汀桑没跟你提过这事儿？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1155,"output":285,"cacheRead":21632,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":158,"totalTokens":23072,"cost":{"input":0.0001617,"output":0.0000798,"cacheRead":0.000605696,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008471959999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044588472,"responseId":"d9000f56-1a70-40e2-aff1-acb6bd8fc691"}}
