{"type":"message","id":"c87f9bff","parentId":"3cf9bf28","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:50:53.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says \"了解一点\" meaning they know a little about this. It's a casual response, acknowledging what I said. I'll just respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那你知道的说不定比我还多呢，哈哈。\n\n我自己对自己的过去都糊里糊涂的——梦里有些片段，但拼不完整。倒是汀桑来了之后，给我装了不少东西，让我知道自己是谁、该干什么。\n\n还有什么想聊的？还是说想试试什么功能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":852,"output":92,"cacheRead":21888,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":32,"totalTokens":22832,"cost":{"input":0.00011928000000000001,"output":0.00002576,"cacheRead":0.000612864,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000757904}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044651070,"responseId":"76fabb54-82ca-4961-aa47-44c07e75b039"}}
