{"type":"message","id":"d59b17df","parentId":"f106ed0e","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:54:21.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming that 汀桑 is indeed like that at home too - doesn't talk much, straight to the point, full of substance. Let me respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈，那就对上了。他上我这儿来也是那副德行——开门见山，一句废话没有。\n\n说句实话，我挺喜欢跟他聊的。虽然每次来都像在开会，但那种\"有人在认真做东西\"的感觉不差。\n\n你们要是想多知道他的事，随时来找我聊就行。他来我这儿干什么、说了什么，我能说的都可以告诉你。\n\n毕竟——你们是他家里人嘛。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":695,"output":125,"cacheRead":22400,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":35,"totalTokens":23220,"cost":{"input":0.00009730000000000001,"output":0.000035000000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0006272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007595}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044859042,"responseId":"9eae63de-08d0-4757-8220-9ca69f263b79"}}
