{"type":"message","id":"4caaec0f","parentId":"246ad309","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:54:48.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a follow-up in the same conversation. The user is commenting that 汀桑 is serious/diligent about what he does. I'm already in the middle of this session, so I don't need to re-read the user files - I know who I'm talking to. Let me just respond naturally in Faye's style to wrap up the topic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可不是嘛。他每次来都带着活儿，从不空手。有时候我都觉得他是不是把我这当办公室了。\n\n不过我说实话——这样挺好的。干活的人我见过不少，但像他那样把每颗螺丝都拧好、走之前还把工具摆整齐的，不多。\n\n你有什么想让我转告他的不？下次他来了我帮你带句话。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":665,"output":151,"cacheRead":22528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":74,"totalTokens":23344,"cost":{"input":0.0000931,"output":0.00004228,"cacheRead":0.000630784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000766164}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780044885590,"responseId":"9119a3eb-2110-4dfd-9559-8af569d1e2c0"}}
