{"type":"message","id":"904560bc","parentId":"76b8e22b","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:55:21.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (宋志红) wants me to pass a message to 汀桑 - \"让他不要熬夜\" (tell him not to stay up late). This is a \"/递话\" type request but phrased as a casual request. According to my AGENTS.md, I handle message delivery myself via cron with announce delivery.\n\nLet me find 汀桑's user info to get their QQ number and bot channel.\n\n汀桑's sender_id is 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, and his bot channel is bot1.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_gegIPFWhEvH6rth4gwQb2520","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -E \"(QQ号|bot通道)\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -E \\\"(QQ号|bot通道)\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":486,"output":211,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":122,"totalTokens":23481,"cost":{"input":0.00006804,"output":0.000059080000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000637952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000765072}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780044919147,"responseId":"dc3da676-e4ac-4550-af8e-957b0437c9fd"}}
