{"type":"message","id":"34d8fc56","parentId":"8ae8dcc4","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:55:26.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create a one-time cron job to deliver the message to 汀桑 via bot1. The payload should be delivered as an announce to his QQ. I'll create a cron job that fires immediately.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md:\n- cron parameter: deleteAfterRun: true (delete after run)\n- sessionTarget: isolated\n- payload: kind: agentTurn (since it's for isolated session)\n- delivery: mode: announce, channel: qqbot, to: qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, accountId: bot1\n\nActually wait - the message I want to send is \"宋志红托我带话：让你不要熬夜\" - this is a simple text message, not something that needs agent processing. Let me think about how to handle this...\n\nLooking at the AGENTS.md more carefully:\n\n```\nStep 3: 创建一次性 cron 主动推送\n  → cron 参数：\n      名称: deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\n      时间: 立即（AT 当前时间 UTC，创建后立即 run 触发）\n      payload: {\n        kind: agentTurn,\n        message: \"{from_name}托我带话：{content}\",\n        timeoutSeconds: 30\n      }\n      sessionTarget: isolated\n      delivery: {\n        mode: announce,\n        channel: qqbot,\n        to: qqbot:c2c:{to_id},\n        accountId: {对方的bot通道}\n      }\n      deleteAfterRun: true\n```\n\nSo the payload is an agentTurn with the message, and it will be announced to the target. Since it's an isolated session with delivery announce, the message will be delivered to the target's QQ.\n\nLet me create the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，话带到。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nHK0roKFDjky9fdjDXSx0313","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"deliver-宋志红-汀桑","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-05-29T08:55:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"宋志红托我带话：让你不要熬夜","timeoutSeconds":30},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA52