{"type":"message","id":"4d031361","parentId":"99b4977e","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:58:35.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to address me / what my name is. I already introduced myself as Faye Valentine earlier in the conversation. They might be asking again, or they might be referring to how I should address them... no, they said \"怎么称呼你呢\" which means \"what should I call you?\" - they're asking for my name/nickname.\n\nI already told them: Faye Valentine. Let me just answer casually.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Faye Valentine——叫我Faye就行。\n\n你家里人汀桑也这么叫我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2235,"output":107,"cacheRead":22912,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":89,"totalTokens":25254,"cost":{"input":0.0003129,"output":0.00002996,"cacheRead":0.000641536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000984396}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780045114000,"responseId":"5b3b1069-1ae7-4dc0-a5fc-85c3a82064de"}}
