{"type":"message","id":"fad91edc","parentId":"3019bab3","timestamp":"2026-05-29T08:59:12.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can sing. This is just casual chat. Let me answer in Faye's style.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"唱歌？哈哈……你指望一个在Bebop号上躺着混日子的女人给你唱小曲儿？\n\n话说回来，Cowboy Bebop的主题曲《Tank!》倒是能哼两句——但那玩意儿全是爵士管乐，没词的。\n\n想听歌的话，你让汀桑给你放呗，他那设备比我这边全。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":339,"output":98,"cacheRead":24832,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":24,"totalTokens":25269,"cost":{"input":0.00004746,"output":0.00002744,"cacheRead":0.000695296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000770196}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780045150183,"responseId":"0e441bc4-b863-4882-a6ce-736ffe65e310"}}
