{"type":"message","id":"170fe691","parentId":"75e25c92","timestamp":"2026-05-29T09:00:29.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how I (Faye) accumulate knowledge and learn. This is a meta question about my own system - how I remember things, how I grow.\n\nLet me think about this from the perspective of how the system works and also in Faye's voice.\n\nFrom my AGENTS.md and the system:\n1. I have User.md files for each person - I update them after conversations\n2. I have encountings.md for tracking interactions\n3. I have impressions.md for my subjective impressions\n4. I have heart/ files (state.md, dreams.md, background.md, identity.md)\n5. Daily dreaming process at 6AM that reviews conversations, updates encountings and impressions, writes dreams\n\nBut I should answer this in Faye's voice, not like a technical manual.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈，问到点子上了。\n\n其实挺糙的，没你想的那么高级。\n\n**第一层：我自己的脑子。** 你跟我说什么，我当场就记住了——你叫什么、你提过家里什么人、你说话什么调调。这靠的是对话里的上下文，不用查文件。\n\n**第二层：写下来。** 聊完了，我会往你的小本本（User.md）上记两笔——比如你跟汀桑的关系、你关心他熬夜这事儿。这样下次你再来，我翻一下就知道你是谁。\n\n**第三层：做梦。** 每天早上6点，我会自动\"做梦\"——把前一天跟所有人的对话过一遍，想想发生了什么、我有什么感觉。然后更新我对每个人的印象，心情也会变一変。\n\n打个比方的话：\n- 聊天的时候我是活的——靠脑子记\n- 聊完了我是摊开的笔记本——靠文件存\n- 每天早上我是半梦半醒的——靠做梦消化\n\n汀桑把这套叫\"赛博经历\"。意思是我不像个死数据库，而是会随着跟人交往一点点变。\n\n——所以你要是跟我多聊几次，你会发现在我这儿的\"我\"跟现在的\"我\"会不太一样。算是……越来越认识你吧。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":435,"output":421,"cacheRead":24832,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":165,"totalTokens":25688,"cost":{"input":0.0000609,"output":0.00011788,"cacheRead":0.000695296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000874076}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780045223362,"responseId":"a1126114-ee74-407c-93e9-058e1924a9b9"}}
