{"type":"message","id":"f3bbb85b","parentId":"ff1ba1bf","timestamp":"2026-05-29T09:49:46.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see 4 photos from today (May 29) that were downloaded - they ended in `_69a18f.jpg`, `_2ebac5.jpg`, `_54d11d.jpg`, and `_2f9b00.jpg`. These are the 4 photos I spawned Son for. Only the first one (7897BED9...) got partially saved to the database.\n\nThe other photos (06B88DD5, 0C0ADC53, 0F56F85B, etc.) are from May 28 - likely from other users or earlier sessions.\n\nSo out of the 4 photos the user sent this session, only 1 got saved (incomplete without AI analysis), and the rest failed due to the qwen API key issue. The user also said they sent 9 photos total - the other 5 must have been sent before the original session's conversation or got lost.\n\nLet me tell the user what happened honestly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，刚才处理照片的时候出了点问题——AI识别图片的那个接口密钥失效了，所以4张照片里只有1张存进去了，而且没识别出具体内容。\n\n要不我直接用我自己的方式帮你存？先把照片文件都收了，回头等汀桑把那个API密钥修好了，我再补个分析。\n\n不过你说传了9张——我这边只收到了4张。其余那些是不是之前传的？可能在网关重启的时候丢了。要不你重新发一遍？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":706,"output":302,"cacheRead":39552,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":200,"totalTokens":40560,"cost":{"input":0.00009884000000000001,"output":0.00008456,"cacheRead":0.001107456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001290856}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780048182483,"responseId":"667c1a07-ff74-446b-8d53-2ff9dc1967c9"}}
