{"type":"message","id":"23bb6bf4","parentId":"ea4440a0","timestamp":"2026-05-29T10:14:57.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son listed the album. All 9 photos are there but all have no annotations since the AI analysis API was broken. Let me just relay this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📖 **你的相册 — 共 9 张**\n\n全是今天存的，不过都没注释——AI识别那个功能暂时坏了，等汀桑修好我再帮你补上。\n\n想看哪张具体的？说 **看照片 0004** 这样就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":49286,"output":90,"cacheRead":8960,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":33,"totalTokens":58336,"cost":{"input":0.0069000400000000005,"output":0.000025200000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00025088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007176120000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780049693286,"responseId":"ff87e3dc-b58d-4f7d-bc0d-4f9a7793ee03"}}
