{"type":"message","id":"21cd8d64","parentId":"f9224c99","timestamp":"2026-05-29T10:35:08.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son returned the Dragon Boat Festival info. Let me forward it to the user in a clean format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"查到了，给你。\n\n## 🐉 端午节资料\n\n**2026年端午节** — 公历 **6月19日（周五）**\n\n### 起源\n- **纪念屈原**（主流说法）—— 楚国诗人投汨罗江，百姓划船投粽子\n- 更早的源头其实是**驱疫避邪**——农历五月是\"毒月\"\n\n### 主要习俗\n| 习俗 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 🛶 赛龙舟 | 划船竞渡，非遗项目 |\n| 🫔 吃粽子 | 甜咸之争，南北不同 |\n| 🌿 挂艾草菖蒲 | 驱蚊辟邪 |\n| 🪢 五色丝线 | 系手腕脚腕，保平安 |\n| 🎒 佩香囊 | 避邪驱瘟 |\n\n### 假期\n按惯例可能会调休三天（6/19 周五～6/21 周日），具体看官方安排。\n\n想查什么具体的可以继续问。😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5505,"output":243,"cacheRead":57472,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":20,"totalTokens":63220,"cost":{"input":0.0007707,"output":0.00006804,"cacheRead":0.001609216,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002447956}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780050905539,"responseId":"25d5265f-3c36-4322-9bed-5ef5dfdc0b2a"}}
